==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dilated
<hw>Di*lat"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Expanded;
enlarged.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Widening into a lamina or into
lateral winglike appendages.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the margin wide and
spreading.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dilatedly</ent>⟦br⟧
